<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavaruṣaṁbulu 1321 Agunēṁṭi phālguna śukla
<lb n="2"/>pavurnnami guruvaramunāṁḍu mahēṁdragiri nāraṇajīyana
<lb n="3"/>koḍku maṁkujīyana tanakunu Abhīṣṭārtthasiddhigānu śrīna
<lb n="4" break="no"/>rasiṁhyanathuni sannidhini veluṁguṭakunu Akhaṁḍadvīpamu
<lb n="5"/>pratimasaitamugānu samarpiṁcenu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> I dvīpāna samarakunu pe
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṭṭina mōdālu yēṁbhaI 50 Ālukhilluri koḍuku dēsikhillāri
<lb n="7"/>vasanaṁ peṭṭenu Itaṁḍu śrībhaṁḍāramaṁdunu nelapaḍi
<lb n="8"/>neI Ēḍu kuṁcālunu Ara 7 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> peṭṭaṁgālāṁḍu Itaniki
<lb n="9"/>kūḍujītamusaitaṁ peṭiri I kuḍujītamu buji
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṁci ĀcaṁdrārkkastāIgānu neI teci peṭaṁgalāṁḍu
<lb n="11"/>I dharmmu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa śrīśrīśrī <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

